0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34749,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/22\/khalil-ibrahim-humility\/","url_meta":{"origin":26949,"position":2},"title":"Wahb on Khalil: Ibrahim was Allah\u2019s best friend for his humility","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Wahb ibn Munabbih reported: I read in some of the books revealed from heaven, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty said to Abraham, upon him be peace: Do you know why I have taken you as an intimate friend? Ibrahim said: No, O Lord. Allah said: For your humility in standing before Me\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26054,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/12\/blessed-content-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":26949,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Contentment: Blessed is one satisfied with Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 12, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn 'Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBlessed is one who is guided to Islam, whose livelihood is sufficient, and who is content with what he has.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2349 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34646,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/06\/bunan-greed-is-slavery\/","url_meta":{"origin":26949,"position":4},"title":"Bunan on Greed: True freedom is contentment, greed is slavery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Zubayr ibn Abdul Wahid reported: Abu al-Hasan Bunan, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe freeman is a slave as long as he is greedy, and the slave is free as long as he is content.\u201d Source: Siyar A\u2019la\u0304m al-Nubala\u0304\u2019 11\/300 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0651\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631 \u0628\u0646 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062d\u0650\u062f\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40808,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/08\/17\/satisfaction-islam-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26949,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Contentment: I am pleased with Allah as Lord","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 17, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says, \u2018I am pleased with Allah as a Lord, with Islam as a religion, and with Muhammad as a messenger,\u2019 he must be given Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1529 Grade:\u00a0Sa